INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (347,'049','✨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 will be a year of honor and prosperity. You will reign over many people and spread your name and fame. Rich in property and clothing, your heart will be at peace and you will enjoy wealth and honor. Fame and fortune are all auspicious, so your name will shine even more. Profit is in distant places, so you will gain opportunities when you go out. With peaceful mind and body, you will accomplish meaningful things and bestow grace upon people in this blessed year.

✨ 2. 💰 Wealth and Financial Fortune
The 2026 financial fortune is very robust. You must well understand the timing to gather and disperse wealth. In March, distinguish well between times to gather and scatter, and invest at appropriate timing. Profit is in distant places, so you can gain wealth through business trips or external activities. In July and August, wealth is everywhere, so move actively. In October and November, you can gain great wealth with benefactor help. Steady savings with the attitude that little drops make the mighty ocean will bring great results.

✨ 3. 🏆 Career and Promotion Fortune
This is a year of great career fortune. In February, like a small dragon ascending to heaven, you will gain fame and spread your name. In April and May, with peaceful mind and body, you will achieve high results and be recognized. In October, benefactors will help so you can achieve great success. In November, good opportunities come from west and south directions, so push forward grandly. Many opportunities for promotion or awards exist, so actively demonstrate your abilities.

✨ 4. ❤️ Love and Marriage Fortune
Love and marriage fortune is good this year. In January, like sun and trees meeting spring, the family is peaceful and glorious. In August, you will meet a beautiful person on a moonlit night with good connections. Joy of family expansion brings daily prosperity. In September, both sides harmonize smoothly, improving marital relations. In December, couples are harmonious and joy fills the home.

✨ 5. 🏥 Health Fortune
Overall health fortune is good this year. Mind and body are peaceful with vitality overflowing and strength abundant. In June, the body regains vitality like all things reviving. However, in July, avoid the eastern direction and don''t overexert. Maintain good condition through stress management and regular lifestyle. Family health is also good, but focus on prevention through regular checkups.

✨ 6. 👥 Relationship Fortune
Relationships are harmonious this year. Treating people sincerely and honestly builds good relationships. In May, don''t tell western people about work content and proceed secretly. In August, joyful things happen through people. In October, benefactor help can bring great achievements, so focus on network management. Treating people with trust leads to blessings.

✨ 7. 📚 Academic and Self-Development Fortune
This is a good year for academics and self-development. In February, gaining fame spreads your name in society. Good results can be expected in certifications or exams. In November, passing exams brings great joy, but preparation must be thorough. Good opportunities come from west and south directions, so push forward grandly and finish boldly. Steady effort leads to good results.','January is a blessed month when sun and trees meet spring. Like flowers and trees flourishing, the home is peaceful and glorious. Family members understanding each other harmoniously - nothing could be better. The family prospers daily, all benefits coming from harmony.

Financial fortune is good. Family harmony leads to financial fortune, so maintain good relations with family. Work can also start the year smoothly. Health is also good for vibrant days. East and south directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being green and pink. Start the new year with a harmonious heart.','February is like a small dragon ascending to heaven. Finally achieving aspirations and rising high, grace overflows. Gaining fame spreads your name in society. However, if results aren''t good, it could become trouble, so act cautiously.

Financial fortune rises. Efforts bear fruit, gaining honor and wealth together. Promotion or award opportunities may arise at work. It''s also a good time for starting business or expansion. Health is good but avoid overwork. The western direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being white and gold.','March is a month to well understand timing of gathering and scattering wealth. Keeping good timing to gather brings great achievements. Mishearing others'' words makes joy and worry half and half, so maintain your stance well. Wealth star follows, so make choices without regret.

Financial fortune is good but requires caution. Judge investment timing well and don''t be easily swayed by others'' words. At work, express opinions clearly but act humbly. For health, stress management is important. The northern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being black and navy.','April is a blessed month of peaceful mind and body. Name is high and deeply meaningful, bestowing grace upon people. Fame can be gained, so both are good fortune. Acting in good timing brings family celebrations and good positions.

Financial and honor fortune rise together. At work, high achievements are recognized with good evaluations. Promotion or important responsibilities may be assigned. Home also has celebrations. Health is good with abundant vitality. The southern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being red and orange.','May is a month requiring caution. Don''t tell western people about work content, proceed secretly. Treat people honestly and sincerely. All directions are unfavorable, so don''t act rashly and judge carefully. Rushing work isn''t good.

